title: Fix the tpu related broken link especially for imagenet_to_gcs.py
body_html:
As you can see in using_tpus, the link of below "a script" is 404 and no longer valid due to tpu-demos repo moved to tpu repo and adjust its correponding structure.

This PR is to fix the below tpu related broken links and also some minor typo.

The TPU-demos repo includes a script for downloading the imagenet dataset

body:
As you can see in [using_tpus](https://www.tensorflow.org/programmers_guide/using_tpu), the link of below "a script" is 404 and no longer valid due to tpu-demos repo moved to tpu repo and adjust its correponding structure.

This PR is to fix the below tpu related broken links and also some minor typo.

> The TPU-demos repo includes [a script](https://github.com/tensorflow/tpu-demos/blob/master/cloud_tpu/datasets/imagenet_to_gcs.py) for downloading the imagenet dataset
